            "text": "Launched atproto publishing a year ago & we've been busy! Since shipped:\n\nsubscribing via atproto\ncustom themes\nquote sharing\nnotifications\nlooseleaf publishing \n@-mentions\nbsky thread viewer\nprofile pages\nstandard.site\nrecommends\nleaflet reader\ncustom fonts\nfootnotes\nanalytics\nnewsletters\n& more!",
